-congregational-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":15651,"position":0},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Congregational Prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"One of you continues to be in prayer as long as he is waiting for prayer.\" --Sunan Abu Dawud 547","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14319,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/an-nawawi-giving-food-break-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":15651,"position":1},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Feeding the Breaking Fast","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Verily, the angels send blessings upon the fasting person...\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/an-nawawi-on-kindness-to-neighbors\/","url_meta":{"origin":15651,"position":2},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Kindness to Neighbors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 23, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Be good to... the near neighbor and the distant neighbor.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/an-nawawi-on-intention-and-sincerity\/","url_meta":{"origin":15651,"position":3},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Sincerity, Good Intentions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Deeds are only be intentions.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20709,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-maintaining-renewing-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":15651,"position":4},"title":"Imam al-Mundhiri on Maintaining and Renewing Ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\"None can preserve his ablution but a believer.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14422,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/an-nawawi-on-thankfulness-and-gratitude-to-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15651,"position":5},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Thankfulness, Gratitude","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Be thankful to me and do not be ungrateful.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias